Troubleshooting Tips
Suricata not capturing traffic:

Verify correct network interface in configuration
Check Suricata is running: sudo systemctl status suricata
Review logs: sudo tail -f /var/log/suricata/suricata.log
Scripts not executing:

Verify execute permissions: chmod +x /opt/soc/scripts/*.py
Check Python path: which python3
Review script errors: python3 -m py_compile script_name.py
No alerts generated:

Confirm log files exist and have content
Verify log paths in scripts match actual locations
Check file permissions: ls -la /opt/soc/logs/
IP blocking not working:

Verify iptables rules: sudo iptables -L -n
Check script has sudo privileges for iptables
Review blocked_ips.log for errors
